=============================
1 编辑web端商家分类管理接口
=============================

1.0 商家分类静态首页 
----------------------

  ::

	 @url /index.php?r=businessCategory/index

	 @method GET

	 @param none

	 @result

1.1 商家分类列表接口
--------------------

  ::
		
		@url  /index.php?r=businessCategory/list

		@method GET

		@param none

		@result  


1.2 商家分类新增
----------------

   ::

	  @url /index.php?r=businessCategory/create

	  @method GET

	  @param
	  
	       :business_category_level:  分类级别(1/2)

		   :business_category_name:   分类名

		   :business_category_color:  分类颜色值

		   :business_category_distacne: 距离值

		   :parent_id:    如果是二级分类要传父分类id

	  @result


1.3 商家分类删除
----------------

    ::

	    @url /index.php?r=businessCategory/delete

		@method get

		@param

		    :business_category_id:     分类id

		@result


1.4 商家分类更新
----------------

    ::

	    @url /index.php?r=businessCategory/update

		@method get

		@param

		   :business_category_id:    分类id

		   :business_category_name:    改后的分类名

		   :business_category_color:  分类颜色值

		   :business_category_distance: 距离


  	    @result


======================
2 二手交易分类接口文档
======================

2.0 二手交易分类静态首页
------------------------

  ::
		
		@url  /index.php?r=secondaryTransactionsCategory/index

		@method GET

		@param none

		@result  


2.1 二手交易分类列表接口
------------------------

    ::

	    @url /index.php?r=secondaryTransactionsCategory/list

		@method GET

		@param

		@result

2.2 二手交易删除接口
--------------------

     ::

	     @url /index.php?r=secondaryTransactionsCategory/delete

		 @method GET

		 @param

		      :second_transaction_categroy_id:   二手交易分类id

		 @result


2.3 二手交易新增接口
--------------------

       ::

	       @url /index.php?r=secondaryTransactionsCategory/create

		   @method GET

		   @param

		        :second_transaction_categroy_name:  分类名(必填)
				:second_transaction_categroy_color: 分类颜色值(可选)

		   @result


2.4 二手交易更新接口
--------------------

        ::

		    @url /index.php?r=secondaryTransactionsCategory/update

			@method GET

			@param
                   
		      :second_transaction_categroy_id:   二手交易分类id
		      :second_transaction_categroy_name:  分类名(必填)
			  :second_transaction_categroy_color: 分类颜色值(可选)


