		@method GET

		@param none

		@result  


3.1 家政分类首页
----------------

      ::

	      @url /index.php?r=category/house

		  @method GET

		  @param

		  @result


3.2 家政分类删除
----------------

      ::

	      @url /index.php?r=category/houseDelete

		  @method GET

		  @param
		      :house_keep_category_id:  家政分类id

		  @result

3.3 家政分类新增页
------------------

       ::

	       @url  /index.php?r=category/houseCreate

		   @method GET

