4 家教分类接口
==============

4.0 家教静态首页
----------------

  ::
		
		@url  /index.php?r=category/homeIndex

		@method GET

		@param

			

		@result  


4.1 家教分类首页
----------------

     ::

	        @url     /index.php?r=category/home

			@method GET

			@param

			@result


4.2 家教分类删除页
------------------

      ::

	      @url   /index.php?r=category/homeDelete

		  @method  GET

		  @param
		  
		      :home_teach_category_id:  家教分类id

		  @result


4.3 家教分类新增页
------------------

      ::

	     @url   /index.php?r=category/homeCreate

		 @method GET

		 @param

		     :home_teach_category_name:  家教分类名
			 
			 :home_teach_category_level: 家教分类级别(1/2)
			 
			 :home_teach_category_pid:  家教分类父id(二级分类需要传)

		@result

4.4 家教分类更新页
------------------

     ::

	    @url    /index.php?r=category/homeUpdate

		@method GET

		@param

		     :home_teach_category_id:  家教分类id
			 
			 :home_teach_category_name:  家教分类名
			 
			 :home_teach_category_order:  家教分类排序字段

	    @result 

